European Energy Market Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project presents an end-to-end analytics pipeline for analyzing European energy markets, combining Python-based data engineering and KPI construction with Power BI interactive dashboards.

The objective was to explore the European energy transition by analyzing energy consumption patterns, renewable energy penetration, fossil fuel dependency, and structural energy efficiency across European countries.

---

## Project Objectives

The project aims to answer the following questions:

- How has European energy consumption evolved over time?
- Which countries are leading the energy transition?
- Which countries remain highly dependent on fossil fuels?
- How can we quantify transition risk across European energy systems?
- Which countries exhibit higher structural energy inefficiencies?

---

## Dataset

The analysis uses publicly available European energy statistics, including:

- Electricity generation
- Electricity demand
- Renewable energy consumption
- Fossil fuel consumption
- Primary energy consumption

Countries analyzed include major European economies and EU member states.

---

